paragraph: Nam Chorios was a planet located in the galaxy's Outer Rim Territories that housed both an Imperial mining colony and prison facility by the fifth year of Darth Sidious' reign as Emperor. The primary star in its planetary system provided barely enough sunshine to illuminate Nam Chorios properly, conferring it a bleak appearance. For that reason, Nam Chorios was considered too cold and unwelcoming by human standards.

title: Namadii
side_bar: {'Astrographical information': {'Region': 'Mid Rim', 'Grid coordinates': 'I-6'}}
paragraph: Namadii was an astronomical object located in the galaxy's Mid Rim, located on a hyperspace route connecting it with Ansion.

title: Nanth'ri
side_bar: {'Astrographical information': {'Region': 'Mid Rim', 'System': "Nanth'ri system", 'Grid coordinates': 'Q-12'}}
paragraph: Nanth'ri was a planet located in the Nanth'ri system within the galaxy's Mid Rim.

title: Naos
side_bar: {'Astrographical information': {'Region': 'Outer Rim Territories', 'Grid coordinates': 'S-18', 'Trade routes': 'Corellian Run'}}
paragraph: Naos was an astronomical object located in the galaxy's Outer Rim Territories, near the rimward end of the Corellian Run hyperspace route.

title: Naporar
side_bar: {'General information': {'Points of interest': ['Chiss Expansionary Fleet medcenter', 'Expansionary Fleet complex', 'Taharim Academy']}, 'Chronological and political information': {'Affiliation': 'Chiss Ascendancy'}}
paragraph: Naporar was a location in the Chiss Ascendancy that contained a medcenter where Mitth'raw'nuruodo underwent physical therapy after the Vagaari pirate operations. Mitth'ali'astov received her sky-walker training at the Expansionary Fleet complex there.

title: Nar Haaska
side_bar: {'Astrographical information': {'Region': 'Outer Rim Territories', 'Sector': 'Hutt Space', 'Grid coordinates': 'T-11'}, 'Physical information': {'Class': 'Terrestrial'}}
paragraph: Nar Haaska was a terrestrial astronomical object located in Hutt Space, within the Outer Rim Territories of the galaxy. It was positioned at the coordinates T-11 on the Standard Galactic Grid.

title: Nar Kaaga
side_bar: {'Astrographical information': {'Region': 'Hutt Space', 'Grid coordinates': 'S-13'}, 'Physical information': {'Points of interest': ['Docking Bay 27-A', "H'unn Cabaret Pit"]}}
paragraph: Nar Kaaga was an astronomical object located in the Hutt Space region of the galaxy. It was connected to fellow Hutt Space world Circumtore and the Bothan Space planet Bothawui by hyperspace routes. Nar Kaaga was located at galactic coordinates S-13.

title: Nazzri
side_bar: {'Astrographical information': {'Region': 'Expansion Region', 'Grid coordinates': 'P-9'}}
paragraph: Nazzri was an astronomical object located in the galaxy's Expansion Region.

title: Neelanon
paragraph: The planet Neelanon was the homeworld of the human senator Terr Taneel, who represented the world Senex in the Galactic Senate of the Republic during the Clone Wars.

title: Neimoidia
side_bar: {'Astrographical information': {'Region': 'Colonies', 'Grid coordinates': 'N-10'}, 'Physical information': {'Fauna': 'Neimoidian tick larva'}, 'Societal information': {'Native species': 'Neimoidian', 'Demonym': 'Neimoidian'}}
paragraph: Neimoidia was a planet centrally located in the galaxy's Colonies region, in grid square N-10 on the Standard Galactic Grid, that was connected to Kattada, Balmorra, and Commenor by a hyperspace route. It was the homeworld of the Neimoidian species, as well as a parasite known as the Neimoidian tick larva, and was near a string of wealthy "purse-worlds" settled by Neimoidians, including Cato Neimoidia. Viceroy Nute Gunray, Settlement Officer Rune Haako, and Senator Lott Dod of the Trade Federation, as well as General Lok Durd and Captain Mar Tuuk of the Confederacy of Independent Systems, were Neimoidians from Neimoidia.

title: Nelvaan
side_bar: {'Astrographical information': {'Region': ['Outer Rim Territories', 'Trailing Sectors'], 'Sector': 'Savareen sector', 'Grid coordinates': 'Q-16', 'Trade routes': 'Triellus Trade Route'}, 'Physical information': {'Climate': 'Frozen', 'Fauna': ['Horax', 'White bantha']}, 'Societal information': {'Native species': 'Nelvaanian', 'Affiliation': 'Techno Union'}}
paragraph: The frigid Outer Rim planet Nelvaan was located in the Savareen sector and was home to the peaceful, sentient Nelvaanian species. During the Clone Wars, the planet's exploitation rights were ceded to the Confederacy of Independent Systems by Onaconda Farr, the Galactic Republic senator of Rodia. The Confederacy-aligned Techno Union used the natives to perform experiments, turning them into cyborg monsters.

title: New Alderaan
paragraph: New Alderaan was a safeworld that the Alderaanian survivor Janray Tessime spent time on during the Galactic Civil War tending to civilian populations.

title: New Apsolon
side_bar: {'Astrographical information': {'Region': 'Mid Rim', 'Grid coordinates': 'P-10'}}
paragraph: New Apsolon was an astronomical object located in the galaxy's Mid Rim.

title: New Cov
side_bar: {'Astrographical information': {'Region': 'Mid Rim', 'Grid coordinates': 'P-14', 'Trade routes': 'Corellian Run'}}
paragraph: New Cov was an astronomical object located in the galaxy's Mid Rim along the Corellian Run.

title: New Holstice
paragraph: New Holstice was a location in the galaxy which had medical facilities associated with the Galactic Republic. The people from New Holstice hosted a monument to Jedi lost in service to the Republic.

title: Nexus Ortai
side_bar: {'Astrographical information': {'Region': 'Mid Rim', 'Grid coordinates': 'Q-14'}}
paragraph: Nexus Ortai was an astronomical object located in the galaxy's Mid Rim.

paragraph: Nimban was a planet located in Hutt Space that was the homeworld of the Nimbanel species.

title: Nirauan
side_bar: {'Astrographical information': {'Region': 'Wild Space', 'Grid coordinates': 'I-5'}}
paragraph: Nirauan was an astronomical object located in Wild Space.

title: Nixor
side_bar: {'Astrographical information': {'Region': 'Mid Rim', 'Grid coordinates': 'Q-12'}}
paragraph: Nixor was an astronomical object located in the galaxy's Mid Rim.

title: Nkllon
